quoteText:
our web server still collects the data that your Internet browser communicates to us (including the IP address of the requesting computer, together with the date, time, the request, which file is requested (name and URL), the amount of data transferred to you, a message as to whether the request was successful, identification data of the browser and operating system used, and the website from which the access was made (should the access take place via a link).

The legal basis of the processing is based on our legitimate interest in ensuring system security, technically administering the website and optimising service quality.
title: Only necessary user logs are kept by the service to ensure quality
